data.description: UPDATE: 95% Complete now DEC '23 remodel 1/2 way between Boeing Everett & Lynnwood Mall, Great low price will benefit you for decades to come. 2 Generous Bedrooms and 2 en suite Full Bathrooms, All new fixtures, tile tub walls, Amazing new Quartz counters shine, all new lower, upper, and bath vanities, this is virtually brand new 2023. water resistant laminate floors throughout, full laundry room, spacious bright deck and storage with mountains / territorial view from penthouse top 3rd floor level, secured power gates at entrance, 1 covered parking spot and loads of guest parking make this a very enjoyable, great exercise with 3 flights of stairs, dogs and cat friendly, you deserve to live here especially with down payment help Available.
